messages.content: 9-1-1, what's your emergency?
Yes, this is Oz County Utilities Emergency Dispatch.
We found a human skull.
Oh my gosh. Where is it located?
I'm going to speak right now with the representative from our field services.
Hi.
Hello, everything is recorded. How are you doing? Do you believe you found a human skull?
Yes, we believe it's human.
What's the location, please?
It's right off of Suburban and Chickasaw in the Kelly Anthony area, right by the school.
Do you have a specific address for me?
No, it's right by the school. If you go straight down, it dead ends right into the woods.
It'll be on the east side of Chickasaw and Suburban.
What is your party's name that we're going to meet with? He's not touching this, I hope.
No, he's a meter reader. Just tell him to stay at that location and stay away from everything.
And if you can, try to stress to him to not draw attention to the area.
Okay.
And you're from what department?
Utilities customer service. If you need any information, my phone number is...
Go ahead and send a call up for a deputy to meet with them.
Okay, we'll see you there very shortly.
What type of vehicle is he going to be in?
Probably a small white Colorado truck with Orange County insignia on it.
Alright, a white Colorado truck with Orange County markings. We'll see you there very shortly.
Alright, thank you.
Bye-bye.
